vnik","_dir":"kroatie-2021","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Dubrovnik","description":"Alles ingepakt, klaar om te gaan! Het weer valt in Nederland momenteel een beetje tegen. Hopelijk hebben we veel zon als we aankomen in Kroatie.","date":"2021-08-21","image":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_164716-scaled-e1631192411229.jpg","category":"Dubrovnik, Hvar, Split, Zadar - Kroatie","intro":"Eindelijk, na anderhalf jaar. Kroatie! Naast een stedentrip door historische steden als Dubrovnik, een bezoek aan de natuurparken zoals de National Park Plitvice en lekker chillen aan de stranden van de Adriatische Zee.","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alles ingepakt, klaar om te gaan! Het weer valt in Nederland momenteel een beetje tegen. Hopelijk hebben we veel zon als we aankomen in Kroatie."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_9900-scaled-e1631193223255.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Yeahh, lets goo."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210826_174450-scaled-e1631192314805.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Doei Nederland!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_9917-scaled-e1631193643787.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"De vlucht duur ongeveer 2 uur."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210826_215650-scaled-e1631192332182.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Na het inchecken even vanuit onze apartement genieten van het uitzicht."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_062813-scaled-e1631192341708.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Goeiemorgen!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_083841-scaled-e1631192347251.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nu lekker wandelen en de stad Dubrovnik verkennen."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_9942-scaled-e1631193243718.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_084114-scaled-e1631192835153.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Deze tredes zijn niet cool... Je ziet ze bijna overal tussen de straatjes door."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_085555-scaled-e1631192368267.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Eindelijk! Old town. Lekker vlak."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_093116-scaled-e1631192372241.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Eerst ontbijt."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_9979-scaled-e1631193248568.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_0063-scaled-e1631193192273.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zoveel snoep!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_103807-scaled-e1631192393196.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wat een uitzicht! Tijd voor lunch?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_0055-scaled-e1631193184788.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lunchtijd! Zwarte Risotto met gebakken calamari."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_111231-scaled-e1631192398795.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Even een break naast de rotsen.. Volgens mij gaat het zo regenen."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_120655-scaled-e1631192402188.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Yeah.. regen."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_143551-scaled-e1631192406891.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Na de regen kwam de zonneschijn. Direct gebruik gemaakt van de kabelbaan om bovenop Mount Srd te komen."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_0078-scaled-e1631193199866.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Helaas moeten we dan ook weer naar beneden. Dit keer lopend, mijn dochter had er geen zin in. Dan maar achterop bij papa."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_0086-scaled-e1631193204534.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Even snel een fototje maken."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/IMG_0100-scaled-e1631193210523.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Beautiful!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_164716-scaled-e1631192411229.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Woah dat was een lange wandeltocht. Laten we hier maar even chillen. Bellevue Beach."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_171235-scaled-e1631193107959.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chillende wijs... tijd voor avondeten?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210828_114331-scaled-e1631193156716.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Avondeten!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_183204-scaled-e1631193145516.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Weer de trappen trotseren om bij ons appartement te komen."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","class":"img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm","src":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20210827_191713-scaled-e1631193151145.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Uitzicht mag er zeker zijn!!"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"de